/IrohLib.xcframework.zip

# The whole xcframework is a build artifact: `xcodebuild -create-xcframework
# -library` (in make_swift.sh) generates the per-slice lib.a + Headers/ plus
# the outer Info.plist from scratch. No hand-laid skeleton is checked in.
